OL,3,CMan drowns in lake while on holiday
OL,4,Cwith girlfriend
OL,6,FA British tourist has drowned in an
OL,7,FItalian lake after getting into
OL,8,Fdifficulty while on holiday with his
OL,9,Fgirlfriend.
OL,11,FSam Rigby, 22, is believed to have
OL,12,Fbeen swimming in Lake Como with
OL,13,Fgirlfriend Olivia Greenall when he
OL,14,Fbegan struggling in the strong current
OL,15,Fon 17 July.
OL,17,FThe pair, from St Helens, were
OL,18,Freportedly sailing towards the town of
OL,19,FMenaggio when they stopped for a swim.
