OL,3,CMan drowns in lake while on holiday
OL,4,Cwith girlfriend
OL,6,FThe couple were then heard shouting
OL,7,Ffor help as they struggled in the
OL,8,Fcurrent before Mr Rigby was swept away.
OL,10,FMiss Greenall, 19, was helped to
OL,11,Fsafety by a passing boat who then
OL,12,Fraised the alarm.
OL,14,FEmergency services carried out an
OL,15,Fintensive search of the area and Mr
OL,16,FRigby's body was recovered from the
OL,17,Fwater later that day after two
OL,18,Fhelicopters and a team of divers
OL,19,Fhelped with the search.
