OL,3,CMan drowns in lake while on holiday
OL,4,Cwith girlfriend
OL,6,FIt is understood Miss Greenall was
OL,7,Ftaken to hospital where she was
OL,8,Ftreated for shock. An investigation
OL,9,Finto Mr Rigby's death has been
OL,10,Flaunched by Menaggio police.
OL,12,FSam and Olivia's former school, St
OL,13,FCuthbert's Catholic High School, paid
OL,14,Ftribute to the pair, saying they
OL,15,F"lived life in all its fullness".
OL,17,FHeadteacher Catherine Twist said: "The
OL,18,Fthoughts and prayers of everyone at St
OL,19,FCuthbert's Catholic High School go out
OL,20,Fto Sam and Liv's families at this
OL,21,Ftragic time.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/6
