OL,6,F"Both students epitomised our school
OL,7,Fmotto of living life in all its
OL,8,Ffullness."JSam's family and friends
OL,9,Falso took to Facebook to pay tribute.
OL,11,FCallum Hill wrote: "RIP Sam no matter
OL,12,Fwhere you are you're always my
OL,13,Fannoying little cousin who always
OL,14,Fwanted to go on video games with me
OL,15,Fand kept asking your mum for me to go
OL,16,Fround to yours.
OL,18,F"What I wouldn't give for us to be
OL,19,Fthat age again just to have one last
OL,20,Fconvo about absolutely anything, miss
OL,21,Fyou mate.
