OL,6,F"Thinking about you all heart goes out
OL,7,Fto your missus too mate, until I see
OL,8,Fyou again."
OL,10,FA spokesman for the UK Foreign Office
OL,11,Fsaid: "We are supporting the family of
OL,12,Fa British man who died in Italy and
OL,13,Fare in contact with the local
OL,14,Fauthorities."
OL,16,FA local police spokesperson said:
OL,17,F"They appear to have dived into the
OL,18,Fwater but their boat was carried away
OL,19,Fand they were unable to get back to it.
